# Project Documentation: AquaGuard Smart Water System

This directory contains the technical documentation for the AquaGuard project, covering system design, mechanical architecture, and project reporting.

## Technical Reports
* **[AquaGuard Report.pdf](AquaGuard_Report.pdf)**: Comprehensive project thesis document including system architecture, mathematical modeling, and final implementation results.

## Visual Design & Renders
* **[212112.PNG](212112.PNG)**: High-resolution 3D render showing the professional component layout and top-side PCB design.

## Schematics
* **System Schematic**: The foundational blueprint of the control circuitry, illustrating the integration of the ATmega328P/ESP8266 and peripheral sensor modules.

---

## Additional Assets
* If additional schematics (e.g., PDF exports from EasyEDA) or datasheets for custom modules are required, they will be archived here.

*Note: For the full fabrication files (Gerbers/BOM), please refer to the `/Manufacturing` directory within the project root.*
